{"tid":1721323,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣新方向\b\b\b】我今日教大家如何「止暴制亂」","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T03:20:58.000Z","uid":22745,"like":74,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"d92461c8e8105e6a2042d2e39bba5c84eeab0404","tid":1721323,"uid":22745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:31:57.000Z","msg":"有鑑於近日政府同藍絲都咁鍾意講「止暴制亂」，我今日就教大家如何止暴，如何制亂。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要點樣先可以止暴制亂？ </span></span><br />\n<strong>捉曬啲示威者？ 二百萬人你捉得曬咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拆大台？ 一早已經無大台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong><br />\n咁應該點做？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好簡單<br />\n就係要政府答應五大訴求</span><br />\n你可能會話 屌 係人都知啦<br />\n<br />\n但係從來都無幾多<em><ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文宣</span></strong></ins></em>係<strong><ins><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">直接清晰</span></em></ins></strong>咁指出過<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n以下係例子<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">/////////////////////////////////////////////////////<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「全港同心 止暴制亂」</span><br />\n<br />\n示威活動停止的方法，只需政府答應五大訴求！<br />\n<br />\n1.全面撤回《逃犯條例》修訂草案<br />\n2.撤回示威「暴動」定性<br />\n3.撤銷被捕示威者控罪<br />\n4.成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5.最重要實現「真雙普選」<br />\n<br />\n答應五大訴求，全港將會回復安穩生活！<br />\n/////////////////////////////////////////////////////</span><br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">簡單來講，我地要將答應五大訴求 同 回復安穩日常 劃上等號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n答應五大訴求＝回復安穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答應五大訴求＝回復安穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答應五大訴求＝回復安穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地要製造 「政府答應五大訴求，黑衣人將會絕跡，再沒有堵路，再沒有獅鳥，再沒有放火，一切都會回復和平安定」 的<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><del><span style=\"color: violet;\">假像</span></del></span>訊息</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n既然佢地都無清晰目標，我地就比個目標佢地。<br />\n佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">既然阻止唔到示威者，就會開始將矛頭指向政府。<br />\n因為只需 答應五大訴求＝即時回復安穩</span><br />\n<br />\n除左香港本土，對外國一樣有用<br />\n唔洗比外國覺得香港示威者走錯方向，<br />\n所以我地要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大大力宣揚 「只需建立民選政府，香港便會回復安穩和平」 的訊息</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n最終，係要洗哂全世界腦<br />\n要<strong>令所有人都覺得 香港要回復和平安定，就只需要建立民主政府 （同答應其餘訴求）</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>人既思考其實可以好單純，特別係藍屍。只要我地「止暴制亂」的方向比政府清晰易明，佢地就會開始調轉槍頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"614d4b969154b0382541482b5f381e58ca9a07ff","tid":1721323,"uid":22745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:32:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d1d0f316c707478dc4805a21f33230207f7a50d","tid":1721323,"uid":22745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:33:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a9258adb10324688b8d1b2ade2e6a4180ac26f4f","tid":1721323,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ce77348d859e06e9e07fd976ffec976b7a399588","tid":1721323,"uid":293225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:34:10.000Z","msg":"推, 雖然P"},{"pid":"34af1968fbde3eb669e008033c12c4b9d02b4946","tid":1721323,"uid":22745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce77348d859e06e9e07fd976ffec976b7a399588","tid":1721323,"uid":293225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T1