lyTime":"2019-11-14T16:18:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43fc7465d4f226c7d08bbd2e504a69303057c833","tid":1721323,"uid":46822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad54f8d4e63a45269168fcee9383e52890695de","tid":1721323,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:19:01.000Z","msg":"我地要全香港黃多過藍，好似中共杯葛法輪功咁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713009</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8a4ee8b59f9644fb9dd25f6c9a27232b5788840e","tid":1721323,"uid":282272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:42:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只有答應五大訴求, 才能回復安穩<br />\n政治問題, 只有政治解決 </span>"},{"pid":"1ce4c95f35fa95f5693b1568d96677327675a7f7","tid":1721323,"uid":45369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d92461c8e8105e6a2042d2e39bba5c84eeab0404","tid":1721323,"uid":22745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:31:57.000Z","msg":"有鑑於近日政府同藍絲都咁鍾意講「止暴制亂」，我今日就教大家如何止暴，如何制亂。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要點樣先可以止暴制亂？ </span></span><br />\n<strong>捉曬啲示威者？ 二百萬人你捉得曬咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拆大台？ 一早已經無大台啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong><br />\n咁應該點做？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">好簡單<br />\n就係要政府答應五大訴求</span><br />\n你可能會話 屌 係人都知啦<br />\n<br />\n但係從來都無幾多<em><ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">文宣</span></strong></ins></em>係<strong><ins><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">直接清晰</span></em></ins></strong>咁指出過<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n以下係例子<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">/////////////////////////////////////////////////////<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「全港同心 止暴制亂」</span><br />\n<br />\n示威活動停止的方法，只需政府答應五大訴求！<br />\n<br />\n1.全面撤回《逃犯條例》修訂草案<br />\n2.撤回示威「暴動」定性<br />\n3.撤銷被捕示威者控罪<br />\n4.成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5.最重要實現「真雙普選」<br />\n<br />\n答應五大訴求，全港將會回復安穩生活！<br />\n/////////////////////////////////////////////////////</span><br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">簡單來講，我地要將答應五大訴求 同 回復安穩日常 劃上等號<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n答應五大訴求＝回復安穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答應五大訴求＝回復安穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答應五大訴求＝回復安穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地要製造 「政府答應五大訴求，黑衣人將會絕跡，再沒有堵路，再沒有獅鳥，再沒有放火，一切都會回復和平安定」 的<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><del><span style=\"color: violet;\">假像</span></del></span>訊息</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n既然佢地都無清晰目標，我地就比個目標佢地。<br />\n佢地<span style=\"color: red;\">既然阻止唔到示威者，就會開始將矛頭指向政府。<br />\n因為只需 答應五大訴求＝即時回復安穩</span><br />\n<br />\n除左香港本土，對外國一樣有用<br />\n唔洗比外國覺得香港示威者走錯方向，<br />\n所以我地要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大大力宣揚 「只需建立民選政府，香港便會回復安穩和平」 的訊息</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------<br />\n最終，係要洗哂全世界腦<br />\n要<strong>令所有人都覺得 香港要回復和平安定，就只需要建立民主政府 （同答應其餘訴求）</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>人既思考其實可以好單純，特別係藍屍。只要我地「止暴制亂」的方向比政府清晰易明，佢地就會開始調轉槍頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T22:59:42.000Z","msg":"有同事每日問我今日嘅訴求係乜嘢"},{"pid":"34e3d6f7137212c80dfa9ff97e73002bca73b7e6","tid":1721323,"uid":22745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T23:18:27.000Z","msg":"有用post無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmo